name: Clean room near Longwood
description:
Small yet functional room with garden and city views, in short walking distance to the Harvard/Longwood Medical Area. Other nearby colleges and institutions include: MCPHS, Northeastern Univ., Wentworth, New England Conservatory, Berklee, Museum of Fine Arts, Fenway Park, Symphony Hall. Green and Orange subway lines are a 5 minute walk away. The room is suitable for a single guest, but can accommodate up to three people in a narrow space. Private refrigerator included.
